Recommends: gir1.2-gkbd-3.0,
            gir1.2-gnomedesktop-3.0
Description: Cinnamon applet with voice input via Whisper
 This package provides a Cinnamon panel applet that combines keyboard
 layout switching functionality with voice input capabilities powered
 by OpenAI Whisper or local Whisper servers.
 .
 Features:
  - Keyboard layout indicator and switcher
  - Microphone button for voice input
  - Support for OpenAI Whisper API
  - Support for local Whisper servers
  - Automatic text insertion via xdotool
  - Configurable recording duration and language
 .
 The applet displays the current keyboard layout and provides quick
 access to voice transcription that types directly into the active window.
